    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:198'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='198:214'>　尚書地理今釋　　　　書𩔖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='214:220'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:241'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案尚書地理今釋一卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='241:264'>　　　國朝蔣廷錫撰廷錫字揚孫常熟人康熙癸未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='264:287'>　　　　進士官至大學士諡文肅是編乃其官内閣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='287:300'>　　　　學士時所作首題</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='300:308'>　聖訓蓋儤直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='308:334'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='334:345'>　　　内廷之日仰承</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='345:368'>　指授敬繕成帙者也其中訂定諸儒之説者如堯典</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='368:391'>　　　　宅嵎夷則據後漢書定為朝鮮正薛季宣于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='391:414'>　　　　欽之誤宅西則據黄度尚書説不限以一地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='414:437'>　　　　正徐廣史記注之誤釐降媯汭則據孔安國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='437:460'>　　　　傳陸徳明釋文之説正水經注媯汭二水之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='460:483'>　　　　誤舜典恒山則據渾源曲陽之道里正漢志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='483:506'>　　　　止曲陽之誤夾右碣石則據顧炎武肇域志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='506:532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='532:555'>　　　　所載劉文偉説正漢志右北平之誤滎波既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='555:579'>　　　　瀦則據傅寅之説正孔𫝊滎波分二水之誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='579:603'>　　　　又訂定蔡沈集𫝊之説者如禹貢治梁及岐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='603:633'>　　　　則據曽<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0776' title='KR0776' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0776.png'/>之説辨其非吕梁狐岐九河既道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='633:656'>　　　　則據經典釋文辨簡潔非一河灉沮既同則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='656:679'>　　　　據元和郡縣志元豐九域志辨此沮水非汳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='679:703'>　　　　沮浮於濟漯則據漢書地理志陳師凱書𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='703:726'>　　　　旁通辨其不知漯水所在濰淄既道則據水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='726:752'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='752:775'>　　　　經注辨淄水不東入濟浮於淮泗則據史記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='775:798'>　　　　河渠書辨禹時泗水上源不自泲通河三江</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='798:821'>　　　　既入則據鄭康成之説辨其誤從庾闡呉都</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='821:844'>　　　　賦注和夷底績則據水經注時瀾書説辨嚴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='844:867'>　　　　道以西無夷道盤庚于今五遷則據史記索</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='867:890'>　　　　隠辨邢即音耿祖乙並未兩遷以及三危有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='890:913'>　　　　二嶓冢亦有二熊耳有二而實一雍梁二水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='913:936'>　　　　兼得岷山荆梁二州各有沱潛黒水有三漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='936:962'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='962:985'>　　　　水有二南亳西亳皆湯所都均考證精核足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='985:1008'>　　　　以證往古之訛釋後儒之惑至於崑崙河源</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1008:1038'>　　　　之説非惟訂漢儒之<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0861' title='KR0861' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0861.png'/>並正元史之非是則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1038:1046'>　　　　恭逢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1046:1069'>　　聖代混一輿圖得以考見其實據尤非前代經師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1069:1082'>　　　　輾轉耳食者比矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1082:1106'>　欽定書經𫝊説已備採其文此蓋其先出别行之本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1106:1122'>　　　　敬著於録俾天下萬世知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1122:1148'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0057', 'WYG', '000-3b' );" name="000-3b" class="pb">[000-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1148:1171'>　聖學髙深度越千古仰觀俯察協契庖犧一時珥筆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1171:1188'>　　　　之臣鞠<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0957' title='KR0957' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0957.png'/></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1188:1197'>　　　螭坳側聆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1197:1220'>　聖訓得餘緒之萬一已能綜括古今為説經家所未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1220:1240'>　　　　曽有也乾隆四十五年七月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1240:1272'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1272:1298'>　　　　　　　　　　總　校　官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸　費　墀</span><br/>
</p>
